.TH "shmem_file_setup" 9 "shmem_file_setup" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
shmem_file_setup \- get an unlinked file living in tmpfs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct file *" shmem_file_setup
.BI "(const char *name "  ","
.BI "loff_t size "  ","
.BI "unsigned long flags "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "name" 12
name for dentry (to be seen in /proc/<pid>/maps
.IP "size" 12
size to be set for the file
.IP "flags" 12
VM_NORESERVE suppresses pre-accounting of the entire object size
